    Page: 195
    Verse: 6
Tags:
  - God
---
He who strives to reach and to accomplish the divine will, will be tried to
the very uttermost; and this is absolutely necessary, for how else could
one acquire that sublime patience without which there is no real wisdom, no
divinity?
